comment.text:
Welcome to Custom Rush. Created by andy6170 and Robert5974
Any time you see a text box with a "?" you can click on it for more information like this.
Tutorial Video: https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=ZaDGV6wWZNs

If you do not use custom spawns for vehicles then I recommend you set them as CALL IN ONLY.

You can ignore the MOD below. On the right you will see the settings for each map. 
The settings are split into 3 sections:
Map Setup
Spawn Locations
Objectives/Sectors

You can use this Template and edit/copy it for other maps.
Settings listed as "OPTIONAL" only give you more control and are not required.
All optional settings below are all default except for Air_Vehicles_Enabled which has been set False.

Read the comments as to what each setting does.

Set the spawn locationd for each team and sector below.
Each sector increases by 1. There is s maximum of 4 sectors (2 MCOM per sector)

Setting a vector to 0.0.0 will use the default base spawns.
Vehicle spawns need to be a different location to players to stop them despawning.

If you you decide not to use custom spawns for vehicles then I recommend making them CALL IN ONLY

You can add additional maps below.
There is the option to have 2 layouts per map. I have done this with Orbital as an example. 
The other maps only have 1 layout.
